    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-11-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-11-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="652"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d652">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Messrs. <persName type="from">Arango, Arias, and
                            Boyd</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 6, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Colon and all the towns of the Isthmus have adhered to the declaration of
                    independence 0proclaimed in this city. The authority of the Republic of Panama
                    is obeyed throughout its territory.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Arango.</hi>
                            </item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Arias.</hi>
                            </item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Boyd.</hi>
                            </item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
